Purchase Cryptocurrencies: Allows users to purchase various cryptocurrencies such as Bitcoin, Ethereum, etc. 
Payment Processing: Accept payments via credit/debit card, bank transfer and other methods to facilitate transactions. 
Cryptocurrency Wallet Integration: Integrate with cryptocurrency wallets to store purchased assets securely. 
API integration: Provide APIs for enterprises and platforms to integrate MoonPay’s services into their applications. 
Global coverage: Provides access to users around the world, supporting multiple languages ​​and currencies. 
User Support: Provide customer support for transaction-related queries and assistance. 
Cooperation: Cooperate with cryptocurrency exchanges, wallet providers and enterprises to expand their service scope. 
Fiat-to-crypto and crypto-to-crypto trading: Enables users to convert between fiat and cryptocurrencies, as well as trade between different digital assets and purchase related products
